                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>A white marble plaque, broken in three connecting fragments, which have been glued back together. Small amounts of surface damage along the breaks, but otherwise complete and well preserved. The rear is very roughly finished, deeply pecked, presumably for attachment to a wall. The front half of the edges is well-finished.</p>
